const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-border text-sm text-muted mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <p class="m-0">
      MIT licensed. Built as part of the broader agentic infrastructure work at
      <a href="https://mabus.ai" class="text-accent no-underline hover:underline">mabus.ai</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="m-0 font-mono text-xs flex gap-3">
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/session-loam" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">github</a>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/session-loam/blob/main/DESIGN.md" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">design</a>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/session-loam/releases" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">releases</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-6 text-xs text-muted/70">
    <p class="m-0">
      The fourth leg next to
      <a href="https://essence.mabus.ai" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">session-essence</a> (identity),
      <a href="https://swarm.mabus.ai" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">swarm-lib</a> (work),
      and <a href="https://tribunal.mabus.ai" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">tribunal</a> (trust).
      Prior art: Maildir + SQLite-backed mail clients (files are durable; the queryable index lives next to them).
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
